WEBVTT

1
00:00:05.466 --> 00:00:07.300
Xiaorong, what are you doing?

2
00:00:07.366 --> 00:00:09.766
Brother, as long as you help me replace Guiying's identity

3
00:00:09.766 --> 00:00:11.166
Qi Niang who became a wife

4
00:00:11.166 --> 00:00:14.166
From now on, the money of their Zhang family will be ours

5
00:00:18.400 --> 00:00:20.700
Why didn't I think of such a good idea?

6
00:00:22.566 --> 00:00:25.066
The daughter's golden lock is mine

7
00:00:25.166 --> 00:00:26.833
I am your mother

8
00:00:27.300 --> 00:00:28.366
How come?

9
00:00:28.400 --> 00:00:31.366
Daughter Golden Lock I have been staying for 20 years

10
00:00:31.366 --> 00:00:34.033
It was their husband and wife who colluded and stole my golden lock

11
00:00:34.166 --> 00:00:35.666
Let's separate our flesh and blood

12
00:00:35.666 --> 00:00:36.900
Can't be reunited

13
00:00:37.566 --> 00:00:39.233
What nonsense are you talking about?

14
00:00:39.500 --> 00:00:41.866
Say who the golden lock belongs to

15
00:00:42.533 --> 00:00:42.766
Right

16
00:00:42.766 --> 00:00:46.166
This golden lock will drive you out of the village if you don't tell the truth

17
00:00:46.166 --> 00:00:49.033
Madam, the gold lock is indeed his

18
00:00:49.666 --> 00:00:51.700
Madam, I'm here to pay off my debt

19
00:00:51.700 --> 00:00:53.700
Just sold his gold lock

20
00:00:53.700 --> 00:00:56.300
I didn't know it was you

21
00:00:56.600 --> 00:00:58.400
A token of recognition

22
00:00:58.566 --> 00:01:00.366
It's all your fault for being obsessed with money

23
00:01:00.566 --> 00:01:02.733
Just let Huiyou pretend to be your mother

24
00:01:02.733 --> 00:01:04.266
That's wrong enough.

25
00:01:05.500 --> 00:01:07.166
You said the golden lock is yours.

26
00:01:07.266 --> 00:01:09.433
What evidence is there?

27
00:01:11.700 --> 00:01:14.400
Fortunately, I had carefully thundered the gold lock before

28
00:01:16.733 --> 00:01:20.700
I carved your name on the inside of a gold lock 20 years ago

29
00:01:21.566 --> 00:01:24.400
Only my mother and I know about this

30
00:01:24.400 --> 00:01:26.666
Is he my biological mother?

31
00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:45.366
Daughter, I finally found you.

32
00:01:48.700 --> 00:01:50.100
What hero is Mengjie?

